# CourseHub API 🚀

An educational RESTful API built with Node.js, Express, MongoDB, and GitHub OAuth.

## 🔗 Live Demo

- 🌐 Render: https://coursehub-api-2bva.onrender.com
- 📘 Swagger UI: https://coursehub-api-2bva.onrender.com/api-docs

## ✅ Features

- Full CRUD: Users, Courses, Categories, Instructors, Enrollments
- Auth: GitHub OAuth + JWT-secured routes (POST, PUT, DELETE)
- Testing: Jest & Supertest with 100% pass rate
- Validation: `express-validator` used for POST & PUT

